EmailTemplate.name: Feedback
EmailTemplate.subject: Thank you for your feedback
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Thank you for taking the time to provide us with your feedback on the Nano App. This is valuable to ensure we continue to offer you the best possible experience.
We review all of the feedback we receive and will reach out if there is an opportunity to discuss further.
If you need to speak to us, please call 13NANO (13 6266). Our business hours are Monday to Friday from 8:30am - 5:30pm AEDT.
Nano Customer Support nano.com.au
